<p id="_04e3bcc7-a8c1-4e6a-cca6-fbbfa22c4de8"><stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mi>f</mi>
    <mrow>
      <mo>(</mo>
      <msup>
        <mtext/>
        <mn>127</mn>
      </msup>
      <msub>
        <mi mathvariant="normal">I</mi>
        <mn>2</mn>
      </msub>
      <mo>)</mo>
    </mrow>
    <mo>=</mo>
    <mn>564074632.42</mn>
    <mo rspace="thickmathspace">⁢</mo>
    <mrow xref="U_MHz">
      <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
        <mi>MHz</mi>
      </mstyle>
      
      
      
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>f (""^{127} I_2) = 564074632.42 "unitsml(MHz)"</asciimath></stem></p>

<p id="_a467da43-663b-a604-4bf2-fe0f7987d2d0">equivalent to</p>

<p id="_abc337e0-aa84-11ad-7cf5-9b578af5a4b2"><stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mstyle mathvariant="italic">
      <mi>λ</mi>
    </mstyle>
    <mo>=</mo>
    <mn>531476582.65</mn>
    <mo rspace="thickmathspace">⁢</mo>
    <mrow xref="U_fm">
      <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
        <mi>fm</mi>
      </mstyle>
      
      
      
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>ii(lambda) = 531476582.65 "unitsml(fm)"</asciimath></stem></p>

<p id="_548062df-ddc2-061c-dcc9-f6801501232a">with an estimated relative standard uncertainty of <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mn>1</mn>
    <mo>×</mo>
    <msup>
      <mn>10</mn>
      <mrow>
        <mo>−</mo>
        <mn>10</mn>
      </mrow>
    </msup>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>1 xx 10^(-10)</asciimath></stem> applies to the radiation of a frequency-doubled diode DFB laser, stabilized with an iodine cell external to the laser with the following parameters:</p>

<ul id="_352fb52b-d8da-18e5-39eb-500e7b14eaf4"><li><p id="_0eaae0de-de47-8300-cafe-4573dc2237a9">cold-finger temperature <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mrow>
      <mo>(</mo>
      <mn>25</mn>
      <mo>±</mo>
      <mn>0.5</mn>
      <mo>)</mo>
    </mrow>
    <mo rspace="thickmathspace">⁢</mo>
    <mrow xref="U_NISTu23">
      <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
        <mi>°C</mi>
      </mstyle>
      
      
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>(25 +- 0.5) "unitsml(degC)"</asciimath></stem> (corresponding to the iodine pressure <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mi>p</mi>
    <mo>=</mo>
    <mn>41</mn>
    <mo rspace="thickmathspace">⁢</mo>
    <mrow xref="U_NISTu12">
      <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
        <mi>Pa</mi>
      </mstyle>
      
      
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>p = 41 "unitsml(Pa)"</asciimath></stem>)</p>
</li>
<li><p id="_4f2d0a13-c124-b4a4-8795-3bce4ceaa0b0">frequency modulation width, peak-to-peak, <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mrow>
      <mo>(</mo>
      <mn>12</mn>
      <mo>±</mo>
      <mn>1</mn>
      <mo>)</mo>
    </mrow>
    <mo rspace="thickmathspace">⁢</mo>
    <mrow xref="U_MHz">
      <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
        <mi>MHz</mi>
      </mstyle>
      
      
      
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>(12 +- 1) "unitsml(MHz)"</asciimath></stem> for <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mn>3</mn>
    <mi>f</mi>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>3f</asciimath></stem> detection cases;</p>
</li>
<li><p id="_c31d1bf8-03ce-e64b-45e2-f2459d827c27">saturating beam intensity of <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mn>12.7</mn>
    <mo rspace="thickmathspace">⁢</mo>
    <mrow xref="U_mW">
      <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
        <mi>mW</mi>
      </mstyle>
      
      
      
    </mrow>
    <mtext> </mtext>
    <mrow>
      <mo>(</mo>
      <mo>±</mo>
      <mn>10</mn>
      <mi>%</mi>
      <mo>)</mo>
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>12.7 "unitsml(mW)"" "(pm10%)</asciimath></stem> at a beam diameter of <stem block="false" type="MathML"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML">
  <mstyle displaystyle="false">
    <mn>1</mn>
    <mo rspace="thickmathspace">⁢</mo>
    <mrow xref="U_mm">
      <mstyle mathvariant="normal">
        <mi>mm</mi>
      </mstyle>
      
      
      
    </mrow>
  </mstyle>
</math><asciimath>1 "unitsml(mm)"</asciimath></stem></p>
</li>
</ul>
</clause>

